addSubElementRef

public boolean addSubElementRef(ElementType e)
Adds a sub-element as a reference. It does not set the container and the formalism. Moreover, it adds this element into referredBy list of the argument element.

Parameters:
e - the element to add.
Returns:
true if the element has been added, false otherwise, sets error accordingly.
